data.description: This spacious double wide mobile home has more than enough to offer! You will appreciate all of the cabinet space, storage closets, stainless appliances, walk-in closets throughout, and the 30x40 shop as well. The home has been very well kept and is in great condition. Plenty of room for 3 car parking under the carport. The back porch is perfect for enjoying a cup of coffee with a nice wooded view. Call today for a private showing to visit this tucked away and peaceful home.  THE ACCURACY OF ALL INFORMATION, REGARDLESS OF SOURCE, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO SQUARE FOOTAGE & LOT SIZE IS DEEMED RELIABLE BUT NOT GUARANTEED AND SHOULD BE PERSONALLY VERIFIED THROUGH PERSONAL INSPECTION BY AND/OR APPROPRIATE PROFESSIONAL.
